m=\"foreign\">ῥέεθρον θαλάσσῃ</foreign>, of a river, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0084.tlg001:49\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.P.\">D.P.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">49</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0084.tlg001:794\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">794</biblScope> </bibl>: hence, seemingly intr., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">νήσοισιν ἐπιπροέηκε</foreign> (sc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">νῆα</foreign>) he <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">made</tr_> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">straight for</tr_> them, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg002.perseus-grc1:15:299\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Od.\">Od.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">15.299</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}